<subSubSection pageId="24" pageNumber="782" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="24.[180,1387,303,775]" pageId="24" pageNumber="782">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[182,531,579,612]" pageId="24" pageNumber="782">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. The Minahassa Pipistrelle is currently known only from the type specimen and a few specimens that have provisionally been attributed to it. Virtually nothing is known aboutits ecology and threats; additional research is needed.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
